
Arkansas might make a quarterback change before playing the Bulldogs on Saturday. Razorbacks coach Houston Nutt hinted as much when answering questions Monday about sophomore Robert Johnson, who has started the first six games but has struggled, particularly in last Saturday's loss to Auburn. Atlanta native Alex Mortensen, son of ESPN NFL analyst Chris Mortensen, is the next in line. But the Razorbacks are being careful not to tip their hand. 

